 ## At a glance (verified 2026-06-16)
 
-- **Integration:** SOAP via `googleads/googleads-php-lib`, API version **`v202602`**; session/auth in `app/Services/AdManager/BaseService.php`; config in `config/google-ads.php` + `config/adManager.php`.
